         <p>The records are arranged chronologically.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <bioghist id="aspace_3942b79df88315918eb298a0665a60bf">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Suite 13, a student group that performed sketch comedy, was founded at Yale in 2000 and disbanded in 2006.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_46d027973bda75185033dc7f80e24cb9">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of administrative files, scripts, and publicity flyers for the productions of Suite 13 at Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
